column1: * The Department requested $99.8 million in the Joint Improvised-Threat Defeat Fund for the FY 2017 November OCO Amendment; however, $87.8 million was appropriated to the Joint Improvised Explosive Device Defeat Fund in Division B of Public Law 114-254.  The Department requests that the $87.8 million be appropriated to the Joint Improvised-Threat Defeat Fund vice the Joint Improvised Explosive Device Defeat Fund.  There are no additional funds requested in the March Amendment for the Joint Improvised-Threat Defeat Fund.  The total FY 2017 OCO Request remains $508.1 million.
